    - "inspect.Signature.bind.__code__.co_argcount == 1 — Signature.bind(self, /, *args, **kwargs) takes 1 positional-or-keyword argument (self); the *args and **kwargs are VAR_POSITIONAL and VAR_KEYWORD parameters not counted in co_argcount. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.Signature.bind.__code__.co_name == 'bind' — the code object co_name for Signature.bind is 'bind'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.Signature.bind_partial.__code__.co_argcount == 1 — Signature.bind_partial(self, /, *args, **kwargs) similarly takes 1 positional-or-keyword argument (self). Verified with Python 3.14.3."
